            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-1">SK Kubang Kerian 3 (SBT)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500 mb-3">Kota Bharu · 1,700 students · 131 staff</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-600">Leading one of Kelantan's largest primary schools with the prestigious <strong>Sekolah Berprestasi Tinggi</strong> (High-Performance School) designation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- School 2: navy accent -->
        <div class="relative flex gap-5 pb-10 group">
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-navy-500 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-navy-50 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true">3rd</div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-navy-100 border-l-4 border-l-navy-400 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-[transform,box-shadow] duration-300 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-gold-500">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-3">
