            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500 mb-3">Kota Bharu · 1,400 students · 115 staff</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-600">Won the <strong>DUTA Award</strong> (Digital Technology Utilisation) at state level in both 2021 and 2022 for digital transformation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- School 3: sage accent (growth) -->
        <div class="relative flex gap-5 pb-10 group">
          <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-sage-500 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center ring-4 ring-navy-50 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true">2nd</div>
          <div class="flex-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-sage-50/40 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-navy-100 border-l-4 border-l-sage-500 hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-[transform,box-shadow] duration-300 focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-gold-500">
