              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-navy-400 uppercase tracking-wider">2014 – 2016</span>
              <span class="bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">National Award</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-1">SK Temalir</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-500 mb-3">Kuala Krai · 250 students · 35 staff</p>
