  </section>

  <!-- Research Teaser -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="md:flex md:items-start md:gap-12">
        <div class="md:w-1/2 mb-8 md:mb-0">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Published Researcher in Educational Resilience</h2>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Most headteachers lead on instinct. Dr. Hamidah built a <strong>mathematical framework</strong> — the Resilient Leadership Index — that turns resilience into something measurable, teachable, and&nbsp;scalable.
          </p>
          <p class="text-navy-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            3 published papers. PhD candidate at UniSZA (final stage). She bridges academic theory and real-world school operations — a combination almost no other candidate&nbsp;offers.
          </p>
          <a href="/research" class="inline-flex items-center text-navy-700 font-medium hover:text-gold-600 transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-gold-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 rounded">
            View Publications →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
          <div class="bg-navy-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-navy-100">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-3">Featured Paper</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-700 font-medium mb-2">"Modelling Resilient Educational Leaders for Resilient Schools: Malaysian High Performing Primary School Head Teachers"</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-navy-500 mb-4">Journal of Management Theory and Practice (JMTP), UniSZA, 2022</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 mb-4">Explores how high-performing headteachers develop resilience during adversity, including the COVID-19 pandemic, through semi-structured interviews with 7 headteachers and 2 education experts across Malaysia.</p>
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.37231/jmtp.2022.3.2.221" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-gold-600 hover:text-gold-700 font-medium">Read Paper →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Social Proof / Quote -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-navy-900">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
